column1: # The V-band luminosities provided by AAVSO
# for MAXI J1820+070 during 58380 to 58440, which are rebined with a bin size of 1 day.
# The uncertainties in the luminosities are quoted at 1-sigma confidence level
# See the methods section for the reduction procedure used to obtain these measurements.
# This file is used to plot the gray points in Panel (C) of Figure 2
# The columns are date in modified Julien date, luminosity and its error
#  The luminosity and its error are in erg/s, taking the source distance D = 2.96 kpc
